com.mesosphere.sdk.offer.taskdata

Class LabelConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mesosphere.sdk.offer.taskdata.LabelConstants

  • final class LabelConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    Names of org.apache.mesos.Protos.Labels to be included in the org.apache.mesos.Protos.TaskInfos of launched tasks. These are accessible to the Scheduler, and/or to custom Executors which we are moving away from ASAP. These are different from environment variables as they are not directly accessible to the running task itself.
